<!-- THE LOWIEZ TASK MANAGEMENT APPLICATION 

Lowiez Task Management Application is a cloud-based task management application. It allows users to manage their tasks from a smartphone, tablet and computer. It is a kind of app that generally used to maintain our day-to-day tasks or list everything that we have to do, with the most important tasks at the top of the list, and the least important tasks at the bottom. It is helpful in planning our daily schedules and cubbing the issues of time wastage at our work places. 

